These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, rock, trance, funk
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of trance and the fan of funk##2
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | funk | rock | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, lemonade, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking water and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | water | 7up | tea | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, horse, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | frog | horse | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kale, apple, grapes
1. the person eating apple is between the person eating kale and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating apple##1
3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | grapes | kale | apple | artichoke |

 #################################

 
